1. *Znak* je simbol koji pokazuje neku poruku ili informaciju. (A sign is a symbol that conveys a message or information.)

2. Znamenitosti našeg grada su *znak* društvenog napretka. (The landmarks of our city are a sign of social progress.)

3. *Znak* je izrazio svoju ljubav prema njoj dugim poljupcem. (He expressed his love for her with a long kiss.)

4. On je dao *znak* sa rukom da bi joj pokazao da ide za njim. (He gave a sign with his hand to show her to follow him.)

5. *Znak* pokazuje da vozilo prolazi kroz železnički kolodvor. (The sign indicates that the vehicle is passing through a railway station.)